        <section id="introduction">
            <h1>Macro Paws Fetish</h1>
            <p>The Macro Paws Fetish focuses on the allure of emphasizing the dynamic between one's immense size and the smaller subjects they interact with. This fetish draws from macro/micro size play, where the exaggerated scale of the paws becomes a symbol of power, dominance, and overwhelming presence. The physical, visual, and thematic impact of macro paws is central to this fetish, blending tactile fantasies with themes of submission and awe.</p>
            <figure>
                <img src="https://static1.e621.net/data/sample/29/9b/299bb99286c52a8181fda2b2b5e6b9be.jpg" alt="Macro Paw Example" class="large-paw-image">
                <figcaption>A towering paw teasingly positioned above a tiny figure. - art by itameowmeow</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>
